  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0bb4\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Weerasumana Weerasinghe has to act with courage to overcome challenges in a critical environment",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "All the political parties that are part of the Parliament should give up narrow political objectives and unite in an all-party government for the sake of the country.",
        "Member of Parliament Weerasumana Weerasinghe said that the leader of the opposition party should know that he must act with courage to overcome the challenges in a critical environment.",
        "Our main demand is that the number of cabinet should be limited to 30 and elections should be held within six months or one year.",
        "All parties, including the Mahanayake Theras, continue to insist on the establishment of an all-party government.",
        "Therefore, all the political parties that are members of the Parliament should unite in an all-party government for the sake of the country, leaving behind narrow political objectives.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition must understand that accepting challenges in critical situations is good leadership.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition is avoiding the formation of an all-party government as he believes that if one of them falls in the government amid the economic crisis, he will also be in crisis.",
        "If an all-party government does not emerge, a weak Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna-led government will re-emerge.",
        "All political parties must understand that the emergence of political crisis again will intensify the economic crisis.",
        "Those involved in the struggle should exercise some patience. The massive damage done to the economy over two and a half years cannot be repaired in a month or two. He said that in the current situation, all the parties should work together."
      ],
